name: Chase, 30cm x 30cm print
description:
Signed and numbered by the artist and in a limited edition of 10, sized 30cm x 30cm, this is a faithful reproduction of the artwork, 'Chase'.

This print has been 'giclee' printed, which is a type of high-quality inkjet printing, regarded as one of the best forms of digital print on the market. Utilising archival inks this print is guaranteed not to fade for over 100 years.

Printed onto 'Somerset Velvet' enhanced white paper 255g/m, which is a beautiful artists paper made from 100% cotton fibres using a traditional mould machine and woollen felts. The paper is naturally acid-free.

The print will be delivered in a cardboard roll.
